  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solution Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Increase&amp;nbsp;team focus on effective communication of vision, requirements, architecture, and design solutions.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No team collaboration. Developers, Testers, Architects, Business Analysts work separately&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Developers create progress reports and documents using manual procedures&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Developers create documents that are not consumable by the team&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No regular review procedure for key artifacts&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Issues and problems are not communicated to the team members&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Creating detailed documentation which is not necessary&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Creating overly detailed design up front&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Poor ties between business strategy and IT solution&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Tools&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Software Architect&amp;reg;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Software Modeler&amp;reg;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; System Architect&amp;reg;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Publishing Engine&amp;reg;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Tools are supported by the following:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Requirements Composer&amp;reg;.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
